///     would finish in 2 seconds, then force-killed it. With no Abort(),
///     you must ensure the thread can actually be interrupted.
///
/// P3: volatile bool is not sufficient for signaling blocked threads.
///     CancellationTokenSource.Cancel() is both thread-safe and observable
///     by blocking APIs.
///
